Putnam, Marion, Alachua points suggest a Middle Archaic occupation. The prehistoric ceramics found suggest a Hickory Pond/Alachua occupation. Also an early 20th century component was present.
Two Middle Archaic points suggest early occupation, while ceramics and other points point to a later Deptford or Alachua occupation. Also early 20th century component present.
Two Clay points and 1 Newnan point suggest early occupation, while ceramics and other points point to a later Deptford or Alachua occupation. Also early 20th century component present.
